(805, '', 'graph_content_creators', 'Members responsible for creating beautiful animated graphics and other things like banners logo, e.t.c for the fumigram company. They will NOT have access to the community\'s admin panel but will receive a beautiful badge on their profile page. Anyone can have this badge if they create something wonderful using fumigram\'s logo or name.'),
(806, '', 'site_lang_translators', 'Members who will help translate the language of fumigram to other languages and correct any errors or misspelled in the site languages. They will NOT be granted access to the admin panel. Anyone can have this badge if they report a few language bugs or errors in the community\'s language'),
(807, '', '_community_promoters', 'Anyone who\'s willing to promote/Advertise or invite their friends and other people to join us on fumigram will receive a badge if this is enabled. Anyone and everyone can have this badge. As a staff member of fumigram you can give anyone this badge if they advertise us. They will NOT have access to the community\'s admin panel or this settings.'),
